{"tid":1270528,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《華爾街日報》:Sony PS5主要強化與大型發行商之間的關係 忽略小型工作室的獨立遊戲","createTime":"2019-07-01T00:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:32:46.000Z","uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7904632c2fc3498a2caff71edc469c66e94565f1","tid":1270528,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:33:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2370149413255566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2370149413255566&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edP195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=a1731bd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2370149413255566</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1JSmaow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1JSmaow.png&h=52e704f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【業界】Sony正在為次世代主機與大型發行商洽談<br />\n<br />\n  據《華爾街日報》報導，Sony正在強化他們與大型發行商之間的關係，備戰次世代主機。<br />\n<br />\n  Sony和Microsoft目前都在準備推出次世代主機，幾個月前，《連線》雜誌曾報導了PS5的大致硬件配置，確認了固態硬盤和向下兼容功能。現在，《華爾街日報》對PS5的軟件方面進行了報導。<br />\n<br />\n  據《華爾街日報》記者Takashi Mochizuki報導，Sony正在集中力量聯繫各大軟件發行商，備戰次世代主機的發售。事實上這並不令人感到意外，<strong><ins>因為PS4已經為Sony積累了大量用戶基礎，已經是各大遊戲發行商較為重視的平台，Sony這一決策能夠揚長避短，擴大優勢。</ins></strong>或許他們能從大型廠商爭取來一些獨占合約。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>  這篇報導中比較有趣的一點是，有許多小型工作室都感覺遭到了Sony的冷遇，相比之下Nintendo更加熱情。</ins></strong>Nintendo Switch發售以來，除了自家少數幾款精品大作以外，很大程度上都多虧了獨立遊戲擴充遊戲庫，因此他們也對獨立遊戲進行了充分支持。<br />\n<br />\n  據Sony官方發言人介紹，<strong><ins>Sony依然歡迎獨立遊戲，但他們目前關心的是強化與大型發行商之間的關係。</ins></strong>Sony相信玩家購買遊戲主機是為了玩到只有這裡才有的高品質遊戲，而不是類似於手機遊戲的同類作品。<br />\n<br />\n  看來Sony在本次時代更迭的關鍵節點選擇的是穩健保守的策略，延續傳統大作的模式，獲得大型廠商的支持，在第一方獨占的基礎下延續PS4的成功。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>[PS5] SomaSim聯合創始人表示 PS5 採用新技術，光線反射將隨處可見</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1257835/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1257835/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>SIE總裁Jim Ryan發表更多關於PS5的信息︰SSD將成為標配、支持4K分辨率下的120Hz</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1187165/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1187165/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>《華爾街日報》記者Takashi Mochizuki：索尼將不會在未來12個月內發售下一代PlayStation主機。</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1126328\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1126328</a>"},{"pid":"b0dc4ac8d5345c748324206db52595fef0174d67","tid":1270528,"uid":37860,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:36:05.000Z","msg":"3廠地獄變補底天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9822cf96602a97d5e58328ea3856c7643870cf4","tid":1270528,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:38:28.000Z","msg":"PS5向下兼容係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d023b57a26f385a8acd09ce4f49939bf32883d3a","tid":1270528,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:13:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Nintendo社長︰Sony對市場上的遊戲內容進行武斷篩選 將會損害遊戲行業的多樣性</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1270540/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1270540/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f6d05ad69340e404b9756733d259e8962415495f","tid":1270528,"uid":78039,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d023b57a26f385a8acd09ce4f49939bf32883d3a","tid":1270528,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:13:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Nintendo社長︰Sony對市場上的遊戲內容進行武斷篩選 將會損害遊戲行業的多樣性</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1270540/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1270540/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:20:04.000Z","msg":"其實都係，剩係ubisoft堆game已經知"},{"pid":"5a6082b8a0a7ed4abfeb33442eb79f8c508a7a2a","tid":127052